        if (t1 = etSubRecordArray) or (t1 = etArray) or (t1 = etMainRecord) or (t1 = etGroupRecord) or (t1 = etSubRecordStruct) or (t1 = etSubRecordArray) or (t1 = etSubRecordUnion)
